                    <h2 class="headings">DISCOVER THE <span>WORLD</span> WITH OUR GUIDE</h2>
                    <p class="lead">
                        Welcome to Explore FATA, your ultimate guide to the former Federally Administered Tribal Areas.
                    <p class="lead">
                        Our mission is to showcase the region's beauty, heritage, and culture.
                    </p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <div class="icons">
                                <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                                <p>20 Years of Experience</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
